  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was also-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] like a film of-- not soot, but you could see sometimes that there is something that created like a film on the grass or-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] or maybe on the concrete, where-- so you knew exactly what-- where it comes from.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When-- when they took my father away, I was totally devastated.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I couldn't stop crying-- same thing with my brother when I didn't see him anymore.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] all I remember is what my father told me to-- you have to be strong in order to survive, no matter what happens.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I followed his advice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Naturally, I mourned, and I was crying.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I felt like-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] like the most precious possession was taken from me, especially when I was-- this was my last link with my father.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] But then I became very bitter and very mad.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and I always-- since then, I always thought, when the time will come and I see them fall, I'm going to take revenge.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I have to stay alive, because I'm going to go out-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] with two machine guns in each-- one machine gun-- and mow all the Germans that I see down.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Many people did that, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But this was then, when I was-- when I was-- you start thinking differently when you become a human being again.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "This is the kind of thinking I was doing when I was reduced to below the grade of an animal.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
